install ollama
1- install ollama and smoke test it :
    curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh
    ollama --version
    ollama pull mistral
    ollama run mistral
    echo "Write a Postgres query to list the 10 most recent transactions." | ollama run mistral

2- Create a specialized “SQL assistant” variant :
    mkdir -p ~/ollama/sql-assistant && cd ~/ollama/sql-assistant
    ollama create moon-mistral-sql -f Modelfile

